<item>
            <title>[FELIX-4368] Support OSGi Repository 1.0 Specification</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-4368</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While logically similar, the Felix OBR does not yet support the OSGi Repository Specification, chapter 132 in the Enterprise R5 spec (&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.osgi.org/Download/Release5&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.osgi.org/Download/Release5&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is a holder issue for this functionality.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12686986">FELIX-4368</key>
            <summary>Support OSGi Repository 1.0 Specification</summary>
